		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">In Flanders Fields</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">This article is about the poem.  For the museum in <a href="/wiki/Ypres" title="Ypres">Ypres</a>, <a href="/wiki/Belgium" title="Belgium">Belgium</a>, see <a href="/wiki/In_Flanders_Fields_Museum" title="In Flanders Fields Museum">In Flanders Fields Museum</a>.  For the book by historian <a href="/w/index.php?title=Leon_Wolff&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Leon Wolff (page does not exist)">Leon Wolff</a>, see <a href="/wiki/In_Flanders_Fields:_The_1917_Campaign" title="In Flanders Fields: The 1917 Campaign">In Flanders Fields: The 1917 Campaign</a>.</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
